Download the socket file online and make the file executable. The important commands are:
svn co http://svn.code.sf.net/p/tango-ds/code/DeviceClasses/Communication/DESY/Socket 
export TANGO_DIR=~/tango/
make


usage: "~/tango/DeviceClasses/Communication/DESY/Socket/tags/Release_1_7/bin/Socket test"
test is a chosen instance name, which can be changed.
